 analysis based on KMeans algorithm. In: 2010 International Conference on Information on Networking and Automation (ICINA). IEEE (2010)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Xu%2C%20J.%2C%20Liu%2C%20H.%3A%20Web%20user%20clustering%20analysis%20based%20on%20KMeans%20algorithm.%20In%3A%202010%20International%20Conference%20on%20Information%20on%20Networking%20and%20Automation%20%28ICINA%29.%20IEEE%20%282010%29\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">23.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR23\">Lukasik, S., Kowalski, P.A., Charytanowicz, M., et al.: Clustering using flower pollination algorithm and Calinski-Harabasz index. In: 2016 IEEE Congress on Evolutionary Computation, Vancouver, 24\u201329 July 2016, pp. 2724\u20132728. IEEE (2016)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Lukasik%2C%20S.%2C%20Kowalski%2C%20P.A.%2C%20Charytanowicz%2C%20M.%2C%20et%20al.%3A%20Clustering%20using%20flower%20pollination%20algorithm%20and%20Calinski-Harabasz%20index.%20In%3A%202016%20IEEE%20Congress%20on%20Evolutionary%20Computation%2C%20Vancouver%2C%2024%E2%80%9329%20July%202016%2C%20pp.%202724%E2%80%932728.%20IEEE%20%282016%29\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">24.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR24\">Bo, F., Wenning, H., Gang, C., et al.: An improved PAM algorithm for optimizing initial cluster center. In: IEEE International Conference on Software Engineering. Service Science. IEEE (2012)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><sp